        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "d9a1744b-f457-4441-9134-7b6d02e8c605",
        "text": "'''Higher Apprenticeship (Level 4/5; equivalent to a Foundation Degree)''': to start this programme, learners should have a Level 3 qualification (A-Levels, Advanced Diploma or International Baccalaureate) or have completed an Advanced Apprenticeship. Higher apprenticeships are designed for students who are aged 18 or over."
      },
